{"tid":1046391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發你個大財囉]高雄市長韓國瑜擬本月下旬訪問港澳及深圳廈門","createTime":"2019-03-04T08:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T08:47:48.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f75070f332c255cab4d118f9f3938f5c9bcdf44c","tid":1046391,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"台灣高雄市長韓國瑜宣布，計劃本月22日至28日訪問香港、澳門、深圳與廈門，進行城市交流，爭取更多的合作機會。他強調，相關行程不會違背台北當局的相關法令規範，希望陸委會放心。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜下午主持高雄市政府兩岸小組首次會議，致詞時宣布外訪計劃。他說，高雄市政府一方面努力加強同中國大陸互動，同時也會努力與東南亞進行經貿合作交流。他希望有關部門能給予高雄市最大支持和鼓勵，讓高雄能夠邁開大步，迎接更多更好的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445927-20190304.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445927-20190304.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4H6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=46e14871\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445927-20190304.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=30bd958b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445927-20190304.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e4657a24f667703560b2cee9a3585d9ff68dd86f","tid":1046391,"uid":50328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:25:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ae2bf62cba2dd85a6a1f8df967fe5a71bc77dc0","tid":1046391,"uid":108133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:47:48.000Z","msg":"香港人去台灣殺人走返黎香港警犬無得拉<br />\n調返轉黎做台灣警察係咪都無得拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}